title: Fear and Family - Robbie Maddison #LIVEARNETTE
description:
FMX is gnarly to begin with, but when you're the one pushing its limits, your next jump could easily be your last. 
In this #LIVEARNETTE video, Robbie talks about his start in motocross, the closeness he felt with Evel Knievel, and how the birth of his son has changed his perspective on what brings him true satisfaction.
